cancelMigration(address,bool).details: Because this function must also be callable by a permissioned migrator, it has an extra migration hook to the nextFundDeployer for the case where cancelMigration() is called directly (rather than via the nextFundDeployer).

params._bypassFailure: True if a failure in either migration hook should be ignored
params._vaultProxy: The VaultProxy contract for which to cancel the migration request
